txt.en: Defeat Orcs and the Trench-captain at Ushkútoz
The Ushkútoz Trenches can be found underneath the scorched ruins of Zudramdân.\n\nYou should defeat Orcs and the Ushkútoz Trench-captain at Ushkútoz.
The Ushkútoz Trenches can be found underneath the scorched ruins of Zudramdân.\n\nYou should defeat Orcs and the Ushkútoz Trench-captain at Ushkútoz.

The Orcs have dug out winding tunnels in the shadow of Zudramdân, further defiling the dwarf-ruin. From these tunnels, they create plans to thwart the Gabil'akkâ vanguard and bolster their own defences. These Orcs of the Ushkútoz Trenches must be removed.
